
<h2>Options when target teacher (<%= targetTeacher.username %>) is busy</h2>
<p>Initiator slot: <%= initiatorSlot.timeSlot %> — <%= initiatorSlot.classGroup %> — <%= initiatorSlot.subject %></p>
<p>Date: <%= new Date(date).toDateString() %></p>

<form method="POST" action="/exchange/request/send">
  <input type="hidden" name="initiatingSlotId" value="<%= initiatorSlot._id %>" />
  <input type="hidden" name="receiverId" value="<%= targetTeacher._id %>" />
  <input type="hidden" name="date" value="<%= date %>" />
  <input type="hidden" name="type" value="cover" />
  <button class="btn">Ask them to cover my slot (they teach same classGroup)</button>
</form>

<hr />
<p>OR — swap one of their slots with yours</p>
<a href="/exchange/select-swap-slot?slotId=<%= initiatorSlot._id %>&targetTeacherId=<%= targetTeacher._id %>&date=<%= date %>">Choose slot of <%= targetTeacher.username %> to swap</a>


